{"tid":1246291,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"我發夢譯左封香港人道歉信","createTime":"2019-06-20T15:48:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T17:07:38.000Z","uid":199319,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ac3f9488c2fddf3bd1097de2b7af94f814759146","tid":1246291,"uid":199319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T15:48:06.000Z","msg":"是咁的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我睇到有人寫左封道歉信比香港人，覺得好撚感動。點解一場抗爭都可以咁有人情味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />雖然小弟係和理非撚，係夢境裡面都無衝前線，但係都好想幫大家做返啲嘢。所以我唯有用自己好少嘅能力譯左英文同德文版嘅 致香港人道歉信，比其他國家嘅嘅人知道香港人真係好可愛。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果有打錯，請指正一下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TMnDiDg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTMnDiDg.png&h=3f7508fd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/orVYiDh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2ForVYiDh.png&h=55f59424&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家如果會上外國forum，麻煩幫忙forward一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBetween, 有無人知點樣可以入文宣組，小弟都想幫下手"},{"pid":"97704090b011e0eaf6348a5d1ea33a26e6c25450","tid":1246291,"uid":170967,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T16:10:02.000Z","msg":"要執執grammar先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過都辛苦晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df8719c183b35ea4df5de4aed90f7c8ecfe3994a","tid":1246291,"uid":222599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T16:54:00.000Z","msg":"加油"},{"pid":"c49b93cdd60cf6f99716bd89fc47d80dbe9f4f40","tid":1246291,"uid":44073,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T16:56:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"074aba201b02a31feaa4b39f1253a9df2c081567","tid":1246291,"uid":206021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T17:02:14.000Z","msg